description: Visybl  built a completely new Asset tracking system using Visybl's Asset beacons and dedicated Asset monitoring CloudNode. Attach our BLE based Asset Beacon to any physical asset you want to track, provision the beacon to your account and use Alexa skill to get  information about their presence, temperature, last known location and time. Visit www.visybl.com to get started.
name: Visybl
shortDescription: Visybl Alexa Skill lets you get status of Visybl beacons attached to your asset
